metadata.name: 738.104.471 | G-Terrain Sculptures
metadata.description:
What is G-Terrain Sculptures?
Re-visualising the natural formations and chemical reactions with computer vision. The base idea is to create a different perception of dimension by re-compiling the natural formations. 

G-Terrain Sculptures generated by AI fed pixel-sorting algorithm. Using python programing language with OpenCV, Keras frameworks and differential color parsing logics.
